Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.02,0:00:15.10,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Dawn comes softer than a sleeping breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:23.08,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(0,0)}Your dream runs through the forest now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:30.09,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(0,200)}You wake up and stir to find the light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:37.93,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}If you've lost it, I'll find it for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:47.40,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,0)}It's hidden in our future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:55.57,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}Now if we joined hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:01:03.29,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}we would go far away without letting go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:11.21,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}In the memory of a far off day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:18.05,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be6\fad(200,200)}the story of the blue country bloomed
