Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:38.87,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}tsutaetai noni damarikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:53.14,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}sakamichi wo sora he noboreba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.55,0:22:59.48,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}wakareyuku suisei no mizuumi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:05.11,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}mikansei na bokutachi dakara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.11,0:23:11.82,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}kizutsukezu ni irarenai
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.66,0:23:17.75,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}dakishimetekuretara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.04,0:23:24.29,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}fureaeru ki ga suru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:30.47,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}dakishimeaetara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:37.06,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}ai suru hito ha kitto soba ni iru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:43.52,ed_romaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}taisetsu na mono wa itsumo soba ni aru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.40,0:22:26.61,ed_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5\fad(200,200)}The two of us who fell for each other
